{"tid":2316720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥質疑許智峯不可信","createTime":"2020-12-08T05:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T07:03:52.000Z","uid":70964,"like":3,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9f1665f504730038e62c862d06a4f7ae4af233ad","tid":2316720,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥回應許智峯及家人戶口被凍結事件，指許智峯是向法庭說謊離港的人，質疑是否要相信他的說話及對本港財政系統的指控。林鄭月娥指，政府做事有規矩，與在社交媒體的發言不同，政府不能過份披露調查進度，否則難以繩之於法，相信銀行亦同樣不能將個人資料攤開予所有人，呼籲判斷某人的說法是否可信時，要考慮他的前科，對來自社交媒體的假資訊，應該極為小心。"},{"pid":"f2c27a1cc65d02e8b6883844d53ac47922272e4d","tid":2316720,"uid":177485,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"唔通信林奠咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359799bc443d7c81d8a1c0ad0b646f61d220b9a8","tid":2316720,"uid":40520,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"香港既第4權又一次證明係垃圾<br />\n成堆記者啞左"},{"pid":"78b2ea06845faffba992a3218429d646d45e466a","tid":2316720,"uid":32220,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"你當初話如果啲人反對你你會辭職而家呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e106bf03e73493788788b0b8f89ad87b271e074","tid":2316720,"uid":70964,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f2c27a1cc65d02e8b6883844d53ac47922272e4d","tid":2316720,"uid":177485,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"唔通信林奠咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"騙子一般都是說謊<br />\n負負得正<br />\n咁即係許智勇是可信的"},{"pid":"eefe06e4fd5cd50b76ab7c9ef5536206dc88ab36","tid":2316720,"uid":130797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"大佬你被制裁緊<br />\n國際恐怖分子黎架<br />\n慳返啖氣縮返入老母個閪度啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e77bc3c59aac8ed20418d1c1